UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The text argues that the “central role” that “nature and culture” play “in shaping the identities of people” is complex, stating that nature and culture “are inextricably linked” and “mutually constituted.”  These ideas are highlighted with the example of the island of Bali, where many people “believe” that the island “possesses a spiritual aura” and “inhabit” the island “with a reverence for its natural beauty and sacred sites.” What is the main idea of this paragraph?',
